            "api_nlt_to_ref": "Ezekiel.24:1-26:21",
            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3EEzekiel%2024%3A1-26%3A21%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_24_1%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2224%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EEzekiel%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E24%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EThe%20Sign%20of%20the%20Cooking%20Pot%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EOn%20January%26%23xA0%3B15%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E24%3A1%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3EOn%20the%20tenth%20day%20of%20the%20tenth%20month%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20the%20ancient%20Hebrew%20lunar%20calendar.%20This%20event%20occurred%20on%20January%26%23xA0%3B15%2C%20588%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-sc%22%3Eb.c.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3B%20also%20see%20note%20on%201%3A1.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20during%20the%20ninth%20year%20of%20King%20Jehoiachin%26%23x2019%3Bs%20captivity%2C%20this%20message%20came%20to%20me%20from%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%3A%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_24_2%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2224%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BSon%20of%20man%2C%20write%20down%20today%26%23x2019%3Bs%20date%2C%20because%20on%20this%20very%20day%20the%20king%20of%20Babylon%20is%20beginning%20his%20attack%20against%20Jerusalem.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_24_3%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2224%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20give%20these%20rebels%20an%20illustration%20with%20this%20message%20from%20the%20Sovereign%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%3A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-sp%22%3E%26%23x201C%3BPut%20a%20pot%20on%20the%20fire%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20pour%20in%20some%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_24_4%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2224%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EFill%20it%20with%20choice%20pieces%20of%20meat%26%23x2014%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ethe%20rump%20and%20the%20shoulder%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20all%20the%20most%20tender%20cuts.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_24_5%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2224%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EUse%20only%20the%20best%20sheep%20from%20the%20flock%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20heap%20fuel%20on%20the%20fire%20beneath%20the%20pot.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EBring%20the%20pot%20to%20a%20boil%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20cook%20the%20bones%20along%20with%20the%20meat.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_24_6%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2224%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BNow%20this%20is%20what%20the%20Sovereign%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20says%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EWhat%20sorrow%20awaits%20Jerusalem%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ethe%20city%20of%20murderers!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EShe%20is%20a%20cooking%20pot%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ewhose%20corruption%20can%26%23x2019%3Bt%20be%20cleaned%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3ETake%20the%20meat%20out%20in%20random%20order%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Efor%20no%20piece%20is%20better%20than%20another.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_24_7%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2224%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EFor%20the%20blood%20of%20her%20murders%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eis%20splashed%20on%20the%20rocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EIt%20isn%26%23x2019%3Bt%20even%20spilled%20on%20the%20ground%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ewhere%20the%20dust%20could%20cover%20it!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_24_8%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2224%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20I%20will%20splash%20her%20blood%20on%20a%20rock%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Efor%20all%20to%20see%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3Ean%20expression%20of%20my%20anger%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20vengeance%20against%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_24_9%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2224%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BThis%20is%20what%20the%20Sovereign%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20says%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EWhat%20sorrow%20awaits%20Jerusalem%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ethe%20city%20of%20murderers!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EI%20myself%20will%20pile%20up%20the%20fuel%20beneath%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_24_10%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2224%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3EYes%2C%20heap%20on%20the%20wood!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3ELet%20the%20fire%20roar%20to%20make%20the%20pot%20boil.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3ECook%20the%20meat%20with%20many%20spices%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20afterward%20burn%20the%20bones.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_24_11%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2224%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3ENow%20set%20the%20empty%20pot%20on%20the%20coals.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EHeat%20it%20red%20hot!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EBurn%20away%20the%20filth%20and%20corruption.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_24_12%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2224%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20it%26%23x2019%3Bs%20hopeless%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ethe%20corruption%20can%26%23x2019%3Bt%20be%20cleaned%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3ESo%20throw%20it%20into%20the%20fire.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_24_13%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2224%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3EYour%20impurity%20is%20your%20lewdness%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20the%20corruption%20of%20your%20idolatry.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EI%20tried%20to%20cleanse%20you%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ebut%20you%20refused.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3ESo%20now%20you%20will%20remain%20in%20your%20filth%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Euntil%20my%20fury%20against%20you%20has%20been%20satisfied.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_24_14%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2224%22%20vn%3D%2214%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E14%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BI%2C%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20have%20spoken!%20The%20time%20has%20come%2C%20and%20I%20won%26%23x2019%3Bt%20hold%20back.%20I%20will%20not%20change%20my%20mind%2C%20and%20I%20will%20have%20no%20pity%20on%20you.%20You%20will%20be%20judged%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20all%20your%20wicked%20actions%2C%20says%20the%20Sovereign%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_24_15%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2224%22%20vn%3D%2215%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EThe%20Death%20of%20Ezekiel%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Wife%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E15%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20this%20message%20came%20to%20me%20from%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%3A%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_24_16%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2224%22%20vn%3D%2216%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E16%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BSon%20of%20man%2C%20with%20one%20blow%20I%20will%20take%20away%20your%20dearest%20treasure.%20Yet%20you%20must%20not%20show%20any%20sorrow%20at%20her%20death.%20Do%20not%20weep%3B%20let%20there%20be%20no%20tears.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_24_17%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2224%22%20vn%3D%2217%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E17%3C%2Fspan%3EGroan%20silently%2C%20but%20let%20there%20be%20no%20wailing%20at%20her%20grave.%20Do%20not%20uncover%20your%20head%20or%20take%20off%20your%20sandals.%20Do%20not%20perform%20the%20usual%20rituals%20of%20mourning%20or%20accept%20any%20food%20brought%20to%20you%20by%20consoling%20friends.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_24_18%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2224%22%20vn%3D%2218%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E18%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20I%20proclaimed%20this%20to%20the%20people%20the%20next%20morning%2C%20and%20in%20the%20evening%20my%20wife%20died.%20The%20next%20morning%20I%20did%20everything%20I%20had%20been%20told%20to%20do.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_24_19%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2224%22%20vn%3D%2219%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E19%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20the%20people%20asked%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BWhat%20does%20all%20this%20mean%3F%20What%20are%20you%20trying%20to%20tell%20us%3F%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%