xport%20orig%3D%22hebr_11_5%22%20bk%3D%22hebr%22%20ch%3D%2211%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EIt%20was%20by%20faith%20that%20Enoch%20was%20taken%20up%20to%20heaven%20without%20dying%26%23x2014%3B%26%23x201C%3Bhe%20disappeared%2C%20because%20God%20took%20him.%26%23x201D%3B%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E11%3A5%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Gen%205%3A24.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20For%20before%20he%20was%20taken%20up%2C%20he%20was%20known%20as%20a%20person%20who%20pleased%20God.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22hebr_11_6%22%20bk%3D%22hebr%22%20ch%3D%2211%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EAnd%20it%20is%20impossible%20to%20please%20God%20without%20faith.%20Anyone%20who%20wants%20to%20come%20to%20him%20must%20believe%20that%20God%20exists%20and%20that%20he%20rewards%20those%20who%20sincerely%20seek%20him.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22hebr_11_7%22%20bk%3D%22hebr%22%20ch%3D%2211%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EIt%20was%20by%20faith%20that%20Noah%20built%20a%20large%20boat%20to%20save%20his%20family%20from%20the%20flood.%20He%20obeyed%20God%2C%20who%20warned%20him%20about%20things%20that%20had%20never%20happened%20before.%20By%20his%20faith%20Noah%20condemned%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world%2C%20and%20he%20received%20the%20righteousness%20that%20comes%20by%20faith.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22hebr_11_8%22%20bk%3D%22hebr%22%20ch%3D%2211%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3EIt%20was%20by%20faith%20that%20Abraham%20obeyed%20when%20God%20called%20him%20to%20leave%20home%20and%20go%20to%20another%20land%20that%20God%20would%20give%20him%20as%20his%20inheritance.%20He%20went%20without%20knowing%20where%20he%20was%20going.%20%3Cverse_e